---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Legal Translation in Dubai â€“ MOJ Certified | OnlineTranslation.ae"
  description="Legal document translation services in Dubai. Contracts, corporate documents, court filings, and litigation support. MOJ-certified for UAE courts and government."
>
  <section class="hero-section bg-dark" data-theme="dark">
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">HOME</a>
        <span class="separator">&gt;</span>
        <span class="current">LEGAL DOCUMENTS</span>
      </nav>
      
      <h1>Legal Document Translation</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">MOJ Certified for UAE Courts</p>
      <p class="hero-intro">Legal documents require precision. Whether you need contracts for business deals, corporate documents for company formation, or translations for court proceedings, every term and clause must be accurately rendered. We handle complex legal terminology with the accuracy that courts and government authorities require.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Corporate Documents</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Company formation, governance, and management documents.</p>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <a href="/legal/corporate/poa/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-signature"></i></div>
          <h3>Power of Attorney</h3>
          <p>General and Special POA for property, banking, and corporate management.</p>
        </a>
        
        <a href="/legal/corporate/moa/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-building"></i></div>
          <h3>Memorandum of Association</h3>
          <p>Mainland and free zone MOA for bank accounts and licensing.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Contracts</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Business agreements and commercial contracts.</p>
      
      <div class="service-grid">
        <a href="/legal/contracts/nda/" class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-lock"></i></div>
          <h3>NDA / Confidentiality</h3>
          <p>Non-disclosure agreements for IP protection and business deals.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container cta-section">
      <h2>Complex Legal Document?</h2>
      <p>Send us your document via WhatsApp for a review. We will assess the complexity, advise on requirements, and provide an accurate quote.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/971508620217" class="btn btn-primary">
        <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Send Your Document
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero-section {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    background: var(--primary-color);
  }
  
  .breadcrumb {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .breadcrumb .separator {
    margin: 0 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }
  
  .breadcrumb .current {
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .hero-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 700px;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }
  
  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .service-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .service-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .service-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
  }
  
  .bg-light .service-card {
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .service-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .service-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
  }
  
  .service-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .cta-section h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .cta-section p {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }
  
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }
  
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--accent-color);
    color: #ffffff;
  }
  
  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #e0144c;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
